        ## Build
        ```bash
        # Using *.sh file on Linux, Unix, OSX
        > ./build.sh
        
        # Using make
        make virtualenv install test
        
        ```
        
        ## Install it from PyPI
        
        ```bash
        pip install g2w
        ```
        
